                                課程簡介
                            

                                 
                            

                                 
                            

                                Introduction
                            





                                多元化的社會裡，每個人基於個人的生活經驗，對事物的看法及追求自身利益，產生了對遊憩的不同使用態度和價值觀，這種相異的行為，自易引發遊憩資源經營、管理及使用上的各種衝突及爭議。　　　　本課程即在揚棄傳統以精英決策的資源管理方式，而改以公眾參與式，並且關註在有效率的公眾參與處理過程，以理性和共有利益為基礎的解決方式。透過調適性經營機制，融入利害關係人協同合作的關係，建構出適合我國處理或解決遊憩衝突的程序。討論議題：公眾參與、遊憩經營、環境政策、環境衝突、衝突解決、跨域整合。

《 課程簡介 -- English 》
                                ln a diversifying society,everyone has different conceptions and senses of value about the use of forests,informed by one's life experiences,opinions of,and self-benefits. Such distinct behavior induces conflicts and disputes over recreationaloperation, as well as the stewardship and usage of forests.　This studies discards traditional resource management ideas and elitedecision-making practices, and focuses instead on public participation. lt focuses on the efficient process of public participation, and utilizes solutionsbased on rational principles and the common interest. With adaptive management, the collaboration of stakeholders can be merged, and a method, which is suitable for settling and resolving recreational conflicts, can beconstituted.Topics: public participation, Recreational management, Environment policy,Environmental conflict, Resolution conflict.











                                Material
                            

                                 
                            

                                上課教材
                            

                                 
                            





                                1.吳國卿譯，（２００５），談判一本通；徹底解決談判最常見的１６個問題，臉譜出版，１９０頁．2.李紹廷澤，（２００７），談判桌上的藝術：為你的人生與事業擔占優勢，商周出版，３１４頁。3.李芳吟譯，（２００５），關鍵對立，美商麥格羅，希爾國際股份有限公司，２９２頁．《參考教材》國家圖書館全國博、碩士論文摘要檢索系統 http://datas.ncl.edu.tw/cgi-bin/theabs.環境資訊中心 http://news.e-info.org.tw/reply/2003. 衝突預防和解決中心 http://www.usda.gov/cprc/美國科羅拉多大學衝突研究協會 http://www.colorado.edu/conflict美國替選爭議解決研究學會 http://www.humboldt.edu/~isadr/cert.htm美國環境的衝突解決學會 http://www.ecr.gov建立一致性的協會網址 http://www.cbi-web.org/content/home.htm美國調解公司 http://www.mediate.com美國衝突解決網絡 http://www.conflict-resolution.netBalint, P.J. Stewart, R.E. Desai, A. and Walters, L.C. (2011) Wicked environmental problems: Managing uncertainty and conflict. Islamdpress PP.253Robbins, P. Hintz, J. and Moore, S.A. (2010) Environment and Society. Wiley-Blackwell. pp.295Maser, C. and Pollio, C.A. (2012) Resolving environmental confilces. (Second edition) CRC Press. Taylor & Francies Group pp.241大師輕鬆讀NO.372，（２０１０），和魔鬼上談判桌，６４頁。











